Package edu.umn.nlpie.mtap.common

Class ConfigImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.umn.nlpie.mtap.common.ConfigImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Config
    public final class ConfigImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements Config
    Global system configuration object.

    By default, will attempt to load a configuration from the following locations:

    1. The MTAP-CONFIG environment variable
    2. $PWD/mtapConfig.yaml
    3. $HOME/.mtap/mtapConfig.yaml
    4. /etc/mtap/mtapConfig.yaml

    Nested objects in the configuration yaml file will be flattened, for example the map: 

       {
     'a' : {
       'b': 1,
       'c': 2
     }
   }
    Will become the map: 
       {
     'a.b': 1,
     'a.c': 2
   }
